SUMMARY:Swarm Workshop: How to Decentralize Any Frontend?
DESCRIPTION:Hands-on workshop by Swarm Foundation.\n\nHost dApps and websites entirely on decentralized infrastructure.\n\nWhat you'll learn:\n• Beeport — web2 rails for Swarm\, upload without running a node\n• Desktop App — your own node for full decentralization\n• Bee light node + Swarm-cli — full terminal control\, scriptable and CI/CD ready\n\nWatch live: https://youtube.com/live/ofsKcDHRgv0\nDiscord support: https://discord.gg/dUS68y87U4
